StringValues.16: A note from Ahyara and Nasun ibn Tifar in the Yaraq Outposts, for delivery to Mara al-Luq outside Yaraq.
StringValues.15: A note from Ahyara and Nasun ibn Tifar for delivery to Mara al-Luq.

Pages.Text:
Mara, we heard of your news.  Congratulations!

- Ahyara

Truly, cause for celebration.

- Nasun ibn Tifar
